{"tid":2135570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇張俊傑話自己當初開龍門炮台山分店係為咗抗衡區內藍店","createTime":"2020-08-01T13:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:19:29.000Z","uid":34572,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f030027e94711ca2772b8995428abe430baffc2","tid":2135570,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"但明明間嘢喺上年六九前已經開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8884b44f333ba98735b5747eadf0d5cceae2d62","tid":2135570,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"#呢篇嘢並唔係一篇告急文<br />\n<br />\n有件事想同大家分享，<br />\n由正苦7月29號決定全港餐廳禁堂食，<br />\n我就決定關閉炮台山分店兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n原因有兩個：<br />\n第一，炮台山分店完完全全追唔上其他龍門分店嘅質素。<br />\n（其實我都要負上極大嘅責任）<br />\n大家都係嚟畀錢食飯嘅，<br />\n我認為無謂要大家含淚去一間唔值得支持嘅分店。<br />\n<br />\n第二，<span class=\"red\">我喺炮台山營業嘅目的，<br />\n係為咗抵抗同一條街唔同嘅藍店，</span><br />\n但自一月起，<br />\n炮台山分店就失去咗附近一班住酒店嘅客人，<br />\n再加上炮台山屬於其中一個疫情重災區，<br />\n喺種種因素下，<br />\n我唯有忍痛將暫停炮台山分店嘅營業時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大家真係唔駛擔心手足、<br />\n姐姐無工開嘅問題，<br />\n表示有心幫我做嘅員工，<br />\n我經已將佢哋調配至其他分店學習。<br />\n如果整體人員水準跟得返，<br />\n又或者當我搵到一套新嘅營運方法<br />\n可以幫到炮台山分店，<br />\n我一定會立即開返舖做生意，<br />\n多謝炮台山友一路以嚟嘅支持！<br />\n<br />\n#呢幾日摸門釘嘅炮台山朋友真係好抱歉<br />\n<br />\n可能性一：張俊傑坐時光機返上年六九前開炮台山分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944931c809c64d61121e7e7bdad7c832cd855a34","tid":2135570,"uid":34572,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqyxGXy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqyxGXy.jpg&h=f78a2880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能性二：啲人坐時光機返去上年六九前寫食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b86ff03a7228232a9bce2b634bebfbdc87e1de","tid":2135570,"uid":101858,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"聾衛兵繼續撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ab17a20cfe39fbdd9790a2be30703a5f0a38b5","tid":2135570,"uid":140548,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"開店目的<br />\n繼續營業目的<br />\n<br />\n標題黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dec216405678b7ee92abd0e8827e490c839f266","tid":2135570,"uid":34572,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9ab17a20cfe39fbdd9790a2be30703a5f0a38b5","tid":2135570,"uid":140548,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"開店目的<br />\n繼續營業目的<br />\n<br />\n標題黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TZ1AkM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TZ1AkM.png&h=0d758d3f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n冇為意佢edit咗啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06400fbd6fd4e0a0655614a276bc5bccb195fc74","tid":2135570,"uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"我喺炮台山營業嘅目的，係為咗賺盡同路人嘅錢。"},{"pid":"c05dc716b3d5a204b8a4e11215c37b227f68fc2b","tid":2135570,"uid":191134,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"不如討論點擴大黃色經濟圈仲好啦 批鬥龍門把撚咩 on99"},{"pid":"1e1f4821bde80cbf868d0ccbf64a3fd4ad4ca746","tid":2135570,"uid":34572,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c05dc716b3d5a204b8a4e11215c37b227f68fc2b","tid":21355